  "bib_entries": {
    "131668383": {
      "title": "A contribution to the study of the Eocene in western Pakistan and western India: Part A, the geology of standard sections in the western Punjab and in the Kohat District",
      "abstract": "Summary Detailed descriptions are given of the geological successions in the Eocene of standard sections in the Rakhi Nala and at Zinda Pir in the western Punjab, and at Tarkhobi, Panoba, the Shekhan Nala and Sirki Paila in the Kohat district. The work forms the first stage in the reinvestigation of the classification and correlation of the Eocene in western Pakistan and western India. Comprehensive collections of fossils were made."
